{"data":[{"date":"07:03 21/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 18h00 ng\u00e0y 21/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/nhan-dinh-nam-dinh-vs-quang-nam-18h00-ngay-217-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam l\u00fac 18h00 ng\u00e0y 21/7 (V\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 18h00 ng\u00e0y 217 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 18h00 ng\u00e0y 217 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/quangnam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span>Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam: 4-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>T\u1eeb ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u00f3ng \u0111inh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i BXH\u00a0V-League 2018, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u201cng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u0111i\u1ec3m\u201d, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 khi m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng b\u01b0\u1edbc sang giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. 7 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 ch\u1ec9 thua 2, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 2, thu v\u1ec1 11/21 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a. Trong khi c\u1ea7n nh\u1edb 2 v\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam ch\u1ec9 ki\u1ebfm v\u1ebbn v\u1eb9n 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1edbi 3-0 song r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, s\u1ef1 non k\u00e9m kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn (b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 3-3).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a n\u00e0y, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi khu v\u1ef1c nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1edd h\u01a1n ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5. Chi\u1ec1u nay, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea3nh th\u01a1i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i h\u01a1n 1 th\u00e1ng (tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Asiad 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi). Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m tay th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u0103ng hoa \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League 2017, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u1ec1u nay, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 6 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac m\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u00f2a 2, thua 5. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 3 tr\u1eadn, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 0, thua 2.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 0, thua 0. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nNam \u0110\u1ecbnh: Qu\u1ed1c Thi\u1ec7n Esele; V\u0103n Qu\u00fd, Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa, H\u1eefu Qu\u00fd, M\u1ea1nh C\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Kortzorg, H\u1eefu \u0110\u1ecbnh, S\u1ef9 Minh, Diogo, Minh Tu\u1ea5n.<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3ng Nam: V\u0103n C\u01b0\u1eddng; V\u0103n Phong, Ng\u1ecdc Nguy\u00ean, V\u0103n H\u00e0, T\u1ea5n Sinh, Thanh Trung, \u0110\u00ecnh Th\u1eafng, Huy H\u00f9ng, Quang Huy, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, Oliveira.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1473","checkdouble":"191707"},{"date":"07:11 21/07","title":"M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u01b0a b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, Fabregas \u0111\u00e3 tranh th\u1ee7 \u201cn\u1ecbnh\u201d t\u00e2n HLV Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/5/9/mua-giai-chua-bat-dau-fabregas-da-tranh-thu-ninh-tan-hlv-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Cesc Fabregas m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea, \u00f4ng Maurizio Sarri.</h2><h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>Cesc Fabregas khen&nbsp;ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri</h2>\r\n<p>Maurizio Sarri&nbsp;l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t ng\u1ed3i l\u00ean chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng HLV CLB Chelsea, sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd, Antonio Conte v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 5 tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, HLV Sarri t\u1eebng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng t\u01b0\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i Napoli v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0m l\u00e1i tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 m\u1edbi h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n theo \u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga Roman Abramovich.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"sarri\" title=\"sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/hlv-sarri-chi-ra-vi-tri-yeu-nhat-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Cesc Fabregas khen ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho t\u00e0i ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m n\u00e0y, Fabregas cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi! \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00edch n\u00f3.&nbsp;T\u00f4i l\u1edbn l\u00ean trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, trong ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 n\u00f3 d\u00e0nh cho m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n trong m\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00ean d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e8 n\u1eb7ng l\u00ean HLV Sarri ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u1edbn h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Napoli. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Chelsea c\u1ee7a Sarri l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi Chelsea s\u1ebd d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi Man City. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm nh\u01b0ng d\u0129 nhi\u00ean HLV Sarri c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1472","checkdouble":"191709"},{"date":"08:00 21/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 21/7): Ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/nhan-dinh-slna-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-217-ghi-diem-truoc-khi-len-tuyen.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa SLNA vs HAGL \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM b\u1edfi d\u00e0n sao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u b\u00ean n\u00e0o s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp trung trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa?</h2><h2>Ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SLNA vs HAGL l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 hai b\u00ean kh\u00e1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c &ndash; Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh c\u00f2n b\u00ean ph\u00eda HAGL c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Vinh trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng SLNA lu\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e1u l\u1eeda v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, c\u1ea3 V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1eabn Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong m\u1eaft th\u1ea7y Park, b\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 217) Ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 217) Ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/Nhan-dinh-SLNA-vs-HAGL-(17h00-ngay-217)-Ghi-diem-truoc-khi-len--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u00eat Nam \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn&nbsp;SLNA vs HAGL s\u1eafp t\u1edbi</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean BXH, m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong m\u1eaft th\u1ea7y Park tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">8 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp cho ASIAD 2018 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i CLB HAGL. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n c\u0169ng \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Vinh s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111ang chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB SLNA l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ef1u binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c. Ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu hai l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chu\u1ed7i 7 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong th\u1eddi gian qua. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1eb3n v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111ang tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea7y m\u00ea ho\u1eb7c, l\u00f4i cu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. C\u00f4ng c\u01b0\u1eddng, th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu nh\u01b0 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 tr\u00ean BXH. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi HAGL s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd n\u00e2ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 8. SLNA \u0111ang &lsquo;bay cao&rsquo; nh\u1edd v\u00e0o c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 1 n\u1ed9i 1 ngo\u1ea1i: Michael Olaha v\u00e0 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. C\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong chu\u1ed7i 7 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 qua c\u1ee7a CLB.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, SLNA c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung V\u0103n B\u00ecnh t\u1eeb FLC Thanh H\u00f3a khi\u1ebfn cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 217) Ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 217) Ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/truc-tiep-hagl-vs-slna-17h00-ngay-265-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB HAGL th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL gi\u00fap h\u1ecd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean HAGL v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. Trong nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Vinh \u1edf 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ra v\u1ec1 tay tr\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015 v\u00e0 2017, Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai &ldquo;\u00f4m h\u1eadn&rdquo; v\u1edbi c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0. Trong khi m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa SLNA vs HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2016 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 1-0 c\u0169ng nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Do v\u1eady n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng, HAGL ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan duy nh\u1ea5t l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u00e1c ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111\u00e3 khi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u0103n nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a HAGL. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA trong c\u00e1c chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa SLNA vs HAGL s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 21/7. Bongda24h s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lich thi dau vong 20 V-League 2018\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Vong-20-V-League.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>SLNA: </strong>V\u0169 H\u1ea3i; Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u00ecnh Ho\u00e0ng, V\u0103n Kh\u00e1nh, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh, Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc, Xu\u00e2n Th\u1eafng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Lynch, Olaha.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>HAGL: </strong>V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n S\u01a1n, A S\u00e2n, A Ho\u00e0ng, Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, V\u0103n Thanh, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, Osmar, Zeba Josip</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: SLNA 2-1 HAGL<br>\r\n</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-vong-20-vleague-dai-chien-slna-hagl-168-191655.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/14/truoc-vong-20-vleague-dai-chien-slna-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-vong-20-vleague-dai-chien-slna-hagl-168-191655.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 20 V-League: \u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn SLNA &ndash; HAGL</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 20 V-League 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111ang d\u1ed3n s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa SLNA vs HAGL, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1471","checkdouble":"191711"},{"date":"08:32 21/07","title":"Th\u1eafng chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, HLV S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/thang-tran-cau-6-diem-hlv-sai-gon-fc-noi-gi-sau-tran.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, HLV S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.</h2><h2>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1\u00a0</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm v\u00f2ng 20 V-League, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 11m c\u1ee7a Ng\u1ecdc Duy \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\" Th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, HLV S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\" Th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, HLV S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/hlv-thanh-cong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng l\u1ea1c quan v\u00e0o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, v\u1ecb HLV v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m l\u00e1i tr\u01b0\u1edfng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n cho hay: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c s\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a XSKT.C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Hi\u1ec7p 1, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i ch\u1eafc, sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 bung l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1. \u0110\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 nh\u01b0 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cTh\u1ef1c ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. Th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 s\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n. B\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh ban \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u01a1i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7p 2 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ee9c n\u00ean v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u201cTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9\u00a0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed1c quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o th\u00eam \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. C\u00f2n v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00ec c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng\u201d, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y n\u00e0y gi\u00fap S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua CLB TP.HCM v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 11 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 19 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t T\u00e2y \u0110\u00f4 r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00f3t b\u1ea3ng. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/can-tho-vs-sai-gon-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191671.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/can-tho-vs-sai-gon-vong-20-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/can-tho-vs-sai-gon-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191671.html\">C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 1-3 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (KT): Thua chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nC\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u00fap S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 20 Nuti Caf\u00e9 V-League 2018, chi\u1ec1u 20/7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1470","checkdouble":"191712"},{"date":"08:32 21/07","title":"HLV FLC Thanh H\u00f3a n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/hlv-flc-thanh-hoa-noi-gi-truoc-tran-tai-dau-ha-noi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 21/7, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</h2><h2>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 tay tr\u1eafng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-4 chung cu\u1ed9c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u1edbi m\u00e0n r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Thanh H\u00f3a d\u00f9 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc song nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i ra v\u1ec1 tay tr\u1eafng.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"FLC Thanh H\u00f3a quy\u1ebft tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"FLC Thanh H\u00f3a quy\u1ebft tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/hlv-duc-thang-va-lanh-dao-flc-thanh-hoa-noi-gi-ve-vu-tram-quan.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u&nbsp;FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Thanh H\u00f3a c\u0169ng \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3 m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef v\u1eefng phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong top 3, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. G\u1eb7p H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng: &ldquo;H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111\u1eb7t ra m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1eb7p ch\u00fat kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi Ng\u00e2n V\u0103n \u0110\u1ea1i v\u00e0 Oseni b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hay kh\u00f4ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 c\u00f3 thua tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng lo m\u1ea5t ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang b\u1ecf xa c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi 14 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 20.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1469","checkdouble":"191713"},{"date":"08:43 21/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (18h00 ng\u00e0y 21/7): Quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/21/nhan-dinh-thanh-hoa-vs-ha-noi-18h00-ngay-217-quyet-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 ch\u1edd ng\u00e0y \u0111\u0103ng quang<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 sau 19 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 qua, CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 c\u1ef1u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch (k\u00e9m t\u1edbi 25 \u0111i\u1ec3m). Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed qu\u00e1n qu\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb l\u00fac n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 14 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam v\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111ang c\u00f3 t\u00e2m trang v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u0103ng quang. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n. Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi, ASIAD s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00fap T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Nhan-dinh-Thanh-Hoa-vs-Ha-Noi-vong-20-V-League-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1eb7t 1 tay v\u00e0o ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u01a1n n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang ng\u1ef1 tr\u1ecb \u1edf \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, nh\u01b0ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3m s\u00fat k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c 2-5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n m\u1edf m\u00e0n giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi\u1ebfu d\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd nh\u1eadn t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 6 b\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc TP. HCM v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh ngay t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n. C\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi x\u1ee9 Thanh ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n xem ra l\u00e0nh \u00edt d\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi Quang H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y xao nh\u00e3ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, m\u01b0a l\u1edbn xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i nay.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"thanh h\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/anh1_1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Thanh h\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i chi\u1ec1u nay s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>X\u1ee9 Thanh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i ti\u1ec7c?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nhi\u1ec1u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t, b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u00f2n nh\u1edb, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 hay nh\u1ea5t t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Thanh H\u00f3a v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Nh\u1eefng si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n trong khung g\u1ed7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh hy v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 th\u00f9 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ede 4 cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea7n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1edbi 10/12 \u0111i\u1ec3m, v\u1edbi 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Thanh H\u00f3a vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/video-tong-hop-thanh-hoa-11-quang-ninh-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111ang b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, khi Thanh H\u00f3a th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 1 trong 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111ang l\u00ean r\u1ea5t cao (th\u1eafng 5, h\u00f2a 2 trong 7 tr\u1eadn), \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u00cdt nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 18 \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khung g\u1ed7, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng &ldquo;\u0111\u00e1nh&rdquo; t\u1edbi t\u1ea5p v\u00ec s\u1edf th\u00edch \u0111i show h\u01a1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0o \u0110T Olympic. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi CLB c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m tin n\u01a1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 - n\u1ebfu anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, bongda24h nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, v\u1edbi b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 Thanh, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u01b0a l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"h\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 20\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/thanhhoa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Pape Omar b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 v\u00ec th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf, trong khi \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu b\u00ean ph\u00eda H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t do nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh H\u00f3a: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng; Xu\u00e2n Th\u00e0nh, Ti\u1ebfn Th\u00e0nh, V\u0103n Nam, Xu\u00e2n H\u01b0ng, V\u0103n Hi\u1ebfu, H\u1eefu D\u0169ng, Ho\u00e0ng Th\u1ecbnh, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00f9ng, Gordon.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: V\u0103n C\u00f4ng; Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, Th\u00e0nh Chung, V\u0103n Ki\u00ean, Moises, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, V\u0103n Th\u00e0nh, Oseni.</div>\r\n<h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 Thanh H\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: 3-2<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-flc-thanh-hoa-noi-gi-truoc-tran-tai-dau-ha-noi-168-191713.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/hlv-flc-thanh-hoa-noi-gi-truoc-tran-tai-dau-ha-noi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-flc-thanh-hoa-noi-gi-truoc-tran-tai-dau-ha-noi-168-191713.html\">HLV FLC Thanh H\u00f3a n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 21/7, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/cdv-nam-dinh-doi-mua-dot-phao-ngay-tai-hang-day-291-191271.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/cdv-nam-dinh-doi-mua-dot-phao-ngay-tai-hang-day.JPEG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/cdv-nam-dinh-doi-mua-dot-phao-ngay-tai-hang-day-291-191271.html\">C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng ngay t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby</span><br>\r\nC\u01a1n m\u01b0a t\u1ea7m t\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m v\u01a1i \u0111i s\u1ef1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League, C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i, trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-vong-20-vleague-dai-chien-slna-hagl-168-191655.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/14/truoc-vong-20-vleague-dai-chien-slna-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-vong-20-vleague-dai-chien-slna-hagl-168-191655.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 20 V-League: \u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn SLNA &ndash; HAGL</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 20 V-League 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111ang d\u1ed3n s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa SLNA vs HAGL, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&nbsp;Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1468","checkdouble":"191714"},{"date":"00:34 21/07","title":"Liverpool ch\u1ea3nh, n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/liverpool-chanh-noi-khong-voi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jurgen Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lyon m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 hai.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, Nabil Fekir c\u0169ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Jean Michael Aulas \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u1ed1i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Liverpool tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool kh\u00f4ng mua Fekir d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lyon ch\u00e0o m\u1eddi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool kh\u00f4ng mua Fekir d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lyon ch\u00e0o m\u1eddi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/liverpool-chanh-noi-khong-voi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool kh\u00f4ng mua Fekir d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lyon ch\u00e0o m\u1eddi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng, ch\u00ednh Lyon c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1ea1t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o, ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean m\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t chuy\u1ec7n gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf \u1edf Anfield.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0ng cho Lyon, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau khi Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf, kh\u1ecfa l\u1eadp th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 v\u1ed3 h\u1ee5t n\u00e0y. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf v\u00f9ng Merseyside \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea1o chi \u0111\u1ebfn x\u1ea5p x\u1ec9 175 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho 4 t\u00e2n binh, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Alisson Becker, v\u1eady n\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n d\u01b0 d\u1ea3 ng\u00e2n qu\u1ef9 cho th\u00eam m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n n\u00e0o n\u1eefa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Jurgen Klopp c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Liverpool s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Fekir n\u1eefa. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi r\u1ed3i, v\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ai n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a CLB.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1467","checkdouble":"191696"},{"date":"01:38 21/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00e2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1i \u1edf Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/Sokratis-Papastathopoulos-991489.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sokratis Papastathopoulos h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd h\u1ebft l\u00f2ng d\u00ecu d\u1eaft v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e0n em \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Konstantinos Mavropanos v\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u1edf Arsenal.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng n\u1eeda n\u0103m m\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Hy L\u1ea1p \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB. Th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Konstantinos Mavropanos b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Emirates v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i s\u00e1u th\u00e1ng sau, Sokratis Papastathopoulos c\u0169ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17,6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Dortmund.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis v\u00e0 Mavropanos c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1ee3 l\u1eabn nhau h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis v\u00e0 Mavropanos c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1ee3 l\u1eabn nhau h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/Sokratis-Papastathopoulos-991489.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis v\u00e0 Mavropanos c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn sau nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e0n anh d\u1ea1n d\u00e0y kinh nghi\u1ec7m, Sokratis c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t ra d\u00e1ng khi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd d\u00ecu d\u1eaft, ch\u1ec9 b\u1ea3o t\u1eadn t\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0n em \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 30 tu\u1ed5i:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Arsenal tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c nhau. V\u00ed d\u1ee5 v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00ec ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y, ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh l\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Dino r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang ta gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Arsenal n\u00ean r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 xem c\u1eadu \u1ea5y thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cN\u1eeda m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Dino g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb m\u1edbi ch\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbt ch\u00e2n r\u00e1o gia nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi cao. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ee1 ng\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec c\u00f3 t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ed3i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111i\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1m v\u00e0 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1466","checkdouble":"191697"},{"date":"04:18 21/07","title":"Neymar tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u00dd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/neymar-tin-ronaldo-se-toa-sang-tren-dat-y.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u00dd, CLB Juventus \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb CLB Chelsea.</h2><h2>Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Chelsea cho trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Chelsea cho trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/13/Juventus-tu-choi-de-nghi-cua-Chelsea-cho-trung-ve-Mattia-Caldara-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara c\u1ee7a Chelsea</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Trong m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, CLB Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara t\u1edbi Juve, tuy nhi\u00ean ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, \u2018L\u00e3o b\u00e0\u2019 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Caldara t\u1eeb Chelsea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>Theo Sky Sport Italia th\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Juve kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch v\u1edbi Caldara v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Juve c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro (27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) cho trung v\u1ec7 Caldara. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Dortmund c\u0169ng g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 35 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng b\u1ecb nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>Trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Juve cho Atalanta m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Anh ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 34 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn L\u00e3o b\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1465","checkdouble":"191698"},{"date":"05:16 21/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 21/7: \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sao PSG li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2015/2/2/Blanc-mo-duong-cho-sao-tre-PSG-den-MU-hinh-anh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sao PSG li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi M.U, Liverpool t\u1eeb b\u1ecf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir, PSG c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Neymar,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 21/7.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sao PSG li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi M.U<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB Man United \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Marquinhos c\u1ee7a PSG. T\u1edd Paris United ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 si\u00eau c\u00f2 Giuliano Bertolucci, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Marquinhos, \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi Man United \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Marquinhos c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi Man United. \u00d4ng Bertolucci \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng d\u00e0nh cho anh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 217 \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sao PSG li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 217 \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sao PSG li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-217-Dai-dien-sao-PSG-lien-he-voi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Marquinhos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 BL\u0110 M.U \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Chelsea sang \u00dd t\u1ef1 tay chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italy, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Chelsea Abramovich v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean gia chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng&nbsp;Fali Ramadani \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Milan \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o&nbsp;Gonzalo Higuain v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd&nbsp;Corriere dello Sport&nbsp;kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Juventus&nbsp;Fabio Paratici \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u00e1i \u0111o\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00f4m 18/7. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n chi 115,9 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y. 69,7 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la cho Higuain v\u00e0 46,2 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la cho Rugani.</p>\r\n<h2>Lamela k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Tottenham</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Erik Lamela l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd m\u1ed9t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u1eadu l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n, giao k\u00e8o n\u00e0y s\u1ebd h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2022. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Heung-min Son c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Tottenham Hotspur.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>T\u00e2n binh Chelsea t\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n h\u00f4m 19/7, t\u00e2n binh Jorginho c\u1ee7a Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n so v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jorginho n\u00f3i: ''C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 hy v\u1ecdng n\u00f3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n n\u00f3&rdquo;. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italy g\u1ed1c Brazil \u0111\u00e1p: ''T\u00f4i th\u00edch ch\u01a1i ngay ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i''.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>PSG c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Neymar<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Qatar cho bi\u1ebft, c\u00e1c \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a PSG s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Kylian Mbappe. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Neymar, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o HLV Thomas Tuchel. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t thanh ti\u1ebfng T\u00e2y Ban Nha&nbsp;El Transistor&nbsp;c\u1ee7a k\u00eanh&nbsp;Onda Cero.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edd AS c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Tuchel kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Neymar b\u1eb1ng Mbappe. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf th\u00edch h\u1ee3p, nh\u01b0&nbsp;Paulo Dybala ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Liverpool r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Liverpool Echo cho hay, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Nabil Fekir trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. T\u1edd b\u00e1o tr\u00ean c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00eam Alisson c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 bom t\u1ea5n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a The Kop \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi bao g\u1ed3m: Shaqiri, Fabinho, Naby Keita v\u00e0 Alissson. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Danny Ward cho Leicester v\u00e0 cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n Daniel Sturbridge. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin sang Real, Hazard v\u1eabn qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi cho Chelsea<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Hazard \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid sau th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 tung ra b\u1ed9 \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o m\u1eabu \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard. Nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V The Blues l\u1ea1i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng sang Real Madrid nh\u01b0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>HLV Enrique \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f9ng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e1o ch\u00ed TBN cho bi\u1ebft t\u00e2n HLV Luis Enrique mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec9nh cao sau ba th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 EURO v\u00e0 World Cup g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 l\u00e0m h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00e0 chinh ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfc Cup ti\u1ebfp theo - EURO 2020 trong hai n\u0103m n\u1eefa'', Enrique chia s\u1ebb trong l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft h\u00f4m 19/7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Zidane kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda l\u00e0m HLV tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2020<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p Noel Le Graet \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho HLV \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m Didier Deschamps sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: &quot;Ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c thay Didier Deschamps. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e8 2020. Ngay c\u1ea3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 k\u00e9m s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Deschamps s\u1ebd t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&quot;.<br>\r\nXEM TH\u00caM:&nbsp;<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-207-184-191687.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 20/7: B\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a HLV Arsene Wenger</span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1464","checkdouble":"191700"},{"date":"05:35 21/07","title":"Real mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201cs\u00e1t th\u1ee7\u201d Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo t\u1edd Marca, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, Mauro Icardi \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</h2><h2>Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Icardi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/17/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-chieu-mo-Icardi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Real Madrid \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, Mauro Icardi</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u00e0 Mauro Icardi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft t\u00e2n binh Alvaro Odriozola, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn\u00a0cho Real v\u00e0 Mauro Icardi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia TBN.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/19, Icardi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 36 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cho Inter. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Icardi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111ang c\u1ea7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, BL\u0110 Real \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Icardi. Real c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1ee9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch PSG ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u1edbi Barca, khi m\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Mauro Icardi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 110 tri\u1ec7u euro.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u00dd \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9 tin CLB Inter \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Icardi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 2023 v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 7,5 \u0111\u1ebfn 8 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a, cao h\u01a1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 5,5 tri\u1ec7u euro \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch Inter chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i Champions League.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2007-180-191661.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2007.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2007-180-191661.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 20/07</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 20/07.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/neymar-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-187-191656.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/neymar-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/neymar-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-187-191656.html\">Neymar ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi PSG d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb CLB Real Madrid.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1463","checkdouble":"191701"},{"date":"05:48 21/07","title":"Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/15/juventus-tu-choi-phu-phang-de-nghi-chuyen-nhuong-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u00dd, CLB Juventus \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb CLB Chelsea.</h2><h2>Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Chelsea cho trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Chelsea cho trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/13/Juventus-tu-choi-de-nghi-cua-Chelsea-cho-trung-ve-Mattia-Caldara-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara c\u1ee7a Chelsea</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Trong m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, CLB Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara t\u1edbi Juve, tuy nhi\u00ean ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, \u2018L\u00e3o b\u00e0\u2019 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Caldara t\u1eeb Chelsea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>Theo Sky Sport Italia th\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Juve kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch v\u1edbi Caldara v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Juve c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro (27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) cho trung v\u1ec7 Caldara. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Dortmund c\u0169ng g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 35 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng b\u1ecb nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>Trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Juve cho Atalanta m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Anh ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 34 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn L\u00e3o b\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1462","checkdouble":"191702"},{"date":"06:10 21/07","title":"\u0110\u00e3 xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/5/da-xong-tuong-lai-tien-dao-son-heungmin.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB Tottenham m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min.</h2><h2>Tottenham gia h\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung-Min\" title=\"Son Heung-Min\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-Min ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Tottenham t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2023</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n b\u00ean ph\u00eda Tottenham \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Anh ghi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 27 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 \u0103n \u00fd khi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ea1nh Dele Alli v\u00e0 Christian Eriksen \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i ngay ph\u00eda sau trung phong Harry Kane.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Son Heung-Min l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap&nbsp;anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn bao g\u1ed3m c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 M.U, Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool. Tuy nhi\u00ean Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00e2n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng x\u1ea5u nh\u1ea5t x\u1ea3y ra.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-minM\u01a1\u0301i \u0111\u00e2y, trang chu\u0309 Tottenham th\u00f4ng ba\u0301o \u0111\u00f4\u0323i bo\u0301ng \u0111a\u0303 gi\u01b0\u0303 ch\u00e2n tha\u0300nh c\u00f4ng Son Heung-min. Ng\u00f4i sao cu\u0309a \u0110T Ha\u0300n Qu\u00f4\u0301c se\u0303 g\u0103\u0301n bo\u0301 v\u01a1\u0301i Spurs \u0111\u00ea\u0301n n\u0103m 2023. \u0110\u00e2y la\u0300 quy\u00ea\u0301t \u0111i\u0323nh quan tro\u0323ng trong b\u00f4\u0301i ca\u0309nh chu\u0309 ti\u0323ch Daniel Levy \u0111ang co\u0301 nhi\u00ea\u0300u tham vo\u0323ng tr\u01b0\u01a1\u0301c mu\u0300a gia\u0309i m\u01a1\u0301i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c Harry Kane v\u00e0 Lamela \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cho th\u1ea5y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Spurs tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ea1ng 3 chung cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi 77 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1461","checkdouble":"191703"},{"date":"06:31 21/07","title":"G\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n 3, Barca quy\u1ebft mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, CLB Barcelona v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 ba \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Willian t\u1eeb Chelsea.</h2><h2>Barca quy\u1ebft mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e2u, ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Sky Sports&nbsp;kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh CLB Barca \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Willian l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh. \u1ede l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 b\u1edfi Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian\" title=\"Willian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/5/Sao-khung-Chelsea-bao-tin-cuc-vui-cho-MU-va-Barca-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB Barcelona g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 h\u1ecfi mua Willian</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u0129 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, Willian \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 M.U v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 Chelsea t\u1ecf ra h\u1edd h\u1eefng v\u1edbi Barca.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Blaugrana \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Willian. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 La Liga \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3, tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi ph\u00eda The Blues kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 Willian \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho M.U, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi HLV Sarri v\u1ec1 Chelsea, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Willian c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Brazil \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin c\u01b0\u0323u c\u00e2\u0300u thu\u0309 Shaktar Donetsk se\u0303 r\u01a1\u0300i Chelsea ngay trong mu\u0300a He\u0300 n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Willian v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n trong 2 n\u0103m n\u1eefa, do \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp sang tu\u1ed5i 30 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/da-xong-tuong-lai-tien-dao-son-heungmin-172-191703.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/5/da-xong-tuong-lai-tien-dao-son-heungmin.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/da-xong-tuong-lai-tien-dao-son-heungmin-172-191703.html\">\u0110\u00e3 xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min</span><br>\r\nCLB Tottenham m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-tu-choi-phu-phang-de-nghi-chuyen-nhuong-cua-chelsea-172-191702.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/15/juventus-tu-choi-phu-phang-de-nghi-chuyen-nhuong-cua-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-tu-choi-phu-phang-de-nghi-chuyen-nhuong-cua-chelsea-172-191702.html\">Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u00dd, CLB Juventus \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb CLB Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1460","checkdouble":"191704"},{"date":"06:42 21/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (21/7/2018